nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.RoboflowRequestData

Packages that use RoboflowRequestData
Package
Description
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data
The nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data package contains the data models used to represent both request and response structures for interacting with the Roboflow API.
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.entity
This package contains the entity classes used to represent the core data structures within the Roboflow API integration.
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.request
This package contains the request classes used to send data to the Roboflow API.
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.request
This package contains classes responsible for constructing and sending HTTP requests to the Roboflow API.
